      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut the <strong>chestnut</strong> <strong>mushrooms</strong> into quarters</p><p>Chop the <strong>leek<span class=\"text-danger\">[s] </span></strong>into rounds, then wash to remove any grit from between the leaves and pat dry with<strong> </strong>kitchen<strong> </strong>paper</p>",
