      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>quartered mushrooms</strong> and <strong>leek rounds </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 5-6 min or until starting to soften</p>",
