      "instruction": "<p>Strip the <strong>rosemary</strong> and <strong>thyme</strong> <strong>leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly together, discard the stems</p><p>Once the mushrooms and leek have started to soften, add the <strong>diced shallot</strong>, <strong>chopped garlic</strong>, <strong>sliced potatoes</strong>,<strong> carrot discs </strong>and <strong>half </strong>the<strong> chopped herbs </strong>(save the rest for later!) to the pan and cook for 3-4 min further</p>",
