    {
      "instruction": "<p>Dissolve the<strong> vegetable stock mix </strong>and<strong> creamy single oat</strong> in 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your<strong> creamy stock</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>creamy stock </strong>to the pan with the <strong>Chinese rice wine </strong>and cook, covered, for 10 min further or until the veg has softened – this is your<strong> veg stew</strong></p>",
